# Business Requirements

**Product-level requirements and scope** live in `docs/business_requirements.md` (problem statement, users, jobs-to-be-done, in/out of scope, success criteria, risks).

Rules:

- Do **not** invent product requirements or expand scope beyond that document, **issues**, **explicit user requests**, or other **checked-in docs**.
- If a change assumes motivation or scope that is not documented, **call that out** in the PR or handoff so owners can confirm.
- When behavior materially shifts who the system serves or what it promises (e.g. new chain class, new trust claims), **update `docs/business_requirements.md`** in the same change when appropriate.
